    "from neuron import h, rxd\n",
    "\n",
    "h.load_file(\"stdrun.hoc\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2024-03-22T10:52:11.769061Z",

    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "dend = h.Section(name=\"dend\")\n",
    "dend.L = 100\n",
    "dend.nseg = 101"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2024-03-22T10:52:11.776216Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2024-03-22T10:52:11.775825Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2024-03-22T10:52:11.781753Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2024-03-22T10:52:11.781271Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def my_initial(node):\n",
    "    if 0.4 < node.segment.x < 0.6:\n",
    "        return 1\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        return 0\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "cyt = rxd.Region(h.allsec(), name=\"cyt\", nrn_region=\"i\")\n",
    "ip3 = rxd.Species(cyt, name=\"ip3\", d=1, initial=my_initial)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2024-03-22T10:52:11.785791Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2024-03-22T10:52:11.784763Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2024-03-22T10:52:12.053388Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2024-03-22T10:52:12.052815Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from matplotlib import pyplot\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def plot_it():\n",
    "    xs = [seg.x * dend.L for seg in dend]\n",
    "    ys = [seg.ip3i for seg in dend]\n",
    "    pyplot.plot(xs, ys)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2024-03-22T10:52:12.056092Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2024-03-22T10:52:12.055840Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2024-03-22T10:52:12.259740Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2024-03-22T10:52:12.259003Z"
    }
   },

      "text/plain": [
       "Text(0, 0.5, '[IP3]')"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 5,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",

   "source": [
    "%matplotlib inline\n",
    "h.finitialize(-65)\n",
    "for tstop in [0, 50, 100, 150]:\n",
    "    h.continuerun(tstop)\n",
    "    plot_it()\n",
    "pyplot.xlabel(\"x (µm)\")\n",
    "pyplot.ylabel(\"[IP3]\")"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "nM = 1e-6  # relative to NEURON's default mM\n",
    "\n",
    "h.finitialize(-65)\n",
    "while dend(0.7).ip3i < 100 * nM:\n",
    "    h.fadvance()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"crossed 100 nM at t = {} ms\".format(h.t))"
   ]
  },

     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "peak ip3 = 0.25437182627374194\n",
      "final ip3 = 0.2103198308254167\n"
     ]

   ],
   "source": [
    "ip3_vec = h.Vector()\n",
    "ip3_vec.record(dend(0.7)._ref_ip3i)\n",
    "t_vec = h.Vector()\n",
    "t_vec.record(h._ref_t)\n",
    "\n",
    "h.finitialize(-65)\n",
    "h.continuerun(1000)\n",
    "max_ip3 = max(ip3_vec)\n",
    "print(\"peak ip3 =\", max_ip3)\n",
    "print(\"final ip3 =\", dend(0.7).ip3i)"
   ]
  }
